c: 20
v: 135
t: Takheun boh tapreh bandum geutanyoe Hana trep jinoe tateupeue bagah Soe tanyoe nyang jak bak jalan teupat Soe nyang Hadharat Neubri hidayah AL-ANBIYA’ (NABI-NABI) JUZ 17) Ngon nama Allah lon peuphon surat Tuhan Hadharat nyang Maha Murah Tuhanku Sidroe geumaseh that-that Donya akhirat rahmat Neulimpah